descriptionHtml:
This is a full list of all game setting variables for TESV. This only includes game settings (those set by \"setgs <name> <value>\"), it does not include global variables (those set by \"set <var> to <value>\").

This list was taken directly from TESV.exe, and it includes a large number of game settings that are not present in the GMST and GLOB lists extractable from Skyrim.esm

Any variable that ends in something like :Audio or :Animation cannot be altered in the game console, but nonetheless it exists.

Obviously there are a bunch of old variables from vegas etc, possibly even oblivion. But I have already confirmed there are a several from Skyrim that don\'t exist in the GMST / GLOB lists (eg iMaxSummonedCreatures, iTrainingNumAllowedPerLevel, etc)
author: DefiniteIntegral
